In Stock

/

Product Dimensions: 6.4"W x 3"H

Power Source: Solar Powered

Age Range (Description): Adult

Room Type: Garden

Shape: Round

# About this item

  * First whole year together, what a gift. To match that opt for a solid brass 1st Anniversary sundial gift handmade in the UK. Grab the gift everybody will wish they’d found first.
  *  With high quality thick brass, our craftsmen combine simplicity, elegance and durability into every single sundial. And for this first wedding anniversary version, they finished it in white. Some may say it’s a bold choice, we say a well-deserved choice. After all, a whole year is something to shout about.
  * DIMENSIONS - Measuring 6.4" across by 3" high, this sundial is just the right size to cast ‘Happy Anniversary. 2023 The First Of Many Wonderful Years together. 1st Wedding Anniversary’ into the very fabric of the metal itself.
  * Each sundial is handmade from real English brass, then coated in two coats of super protective lacquer. This locks in the shine, keeps the white whiter than white and means the lucky beneficiary needn’t lift a finger. You may want to give it a wipe when visiting though, to look busy.
  * As well as a gnomon (yep, the triangular part of a sundial that casts a shadow has a name), all sundials come with a stand for displaying on a shelf indoors and three required screws. For outdoor mounting check out our Sundial Pedestal option.
